Author: Alex Landau
Author-email: balexlandau@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: 
        Cachual
        -------
        
        Cachual is a simple library that makes it easy to cache the return values from
        your python functions with an annotation::
        
            cache = RedisCache()
            
            @cache.cached(ttl=900)
            def is_user_valid(user_id):
                ...
        
Platform: any
